  <name>Radeon Profile</name>
  <summary>Simple application to read current clocks of ATi Radeon cards (xf86-video-ati, xf86-video-amdgpu).</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Radeon profile is an user friendly application that allows to read GPU usage, clocks and temperature, manage power profiles and fan speed (on HD7000 series cards and above) and overclock your GPU (on Amdgpu driver).</p>
    <p>Radeon profile works with the open source Radeon driver (xf86-video-ati) and the Amdgpu driver (xf86-video-amdgpu or Amdgpu-Pro).</p>
  </description>
